participants.title: Lead Technical Recruiter at nTech Solutions

messages.message:
Solutions Architect Needed

Good Morning Brian,

I'm Jenna Wolfe, a Technical Recruiter with nTech Solutions. I'm reaching out today about an open Solutions Architect role with my client in Baltimore, MD. 

Given your lengthy list of preferred locations, I figured it wouldn't hurt to just check in and see if you may be open to the East Coast. 

This would be a 12-24 month contract with Exelon. If you have any interest or know of someone else who may be interested, please let me know the best email to send the full job description. 

Thank you,
Jenna

Jenna Wolfe
jenna@ntechsol.com
Sorry not interested in working for a recruiting agency.
